    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Foreclosure Fairness Act of 2014 - Prohibits a court, in the case of any federally related mortgage loan made after enactment of this Act, from entering a deficiency judgment requiring the mortgagor to pay any balance on the mortgage loan after a foreclosure sale of the mortgaged property.</p>]]></text>
